videos.headline: Oshie: 'Momentum is on our side'
videos.description: T.J. Oshie chats with Steve Levy about the 10-minute misconduct at the end of the game, resting up before Game 5 and his Metro card struggles.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Oshie: 'Momentum is on our side') 2018/06/4

videos.headline: Capitals on the brink of franchise history
videos.description: Greg Wyshynski believes Washington will the Stanley Cup in Game 5, while Emily Kaplan says Vegas will extend the series just one more game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Analysis (Capitals on the brink of franchise history) 2018/06/04

videos.headline: Neal on almost goal: Game changes if I score
videos.description: James Neal reacts to his first-period shot that bounced off the post in Vegas' Game 4 loss, and he says he expects the team to regroup for Game 5.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Neal on almost goal: Game changes if I score) 2018/06/04
